This is Diwen Chen's IMGD 4300 Final Project - Boids Simulation.
A 3d Boids simulation without using helper libraries. 
User may drag the camera, repel/attract boids, and adjust the parameters. 
The theme is Order & Chaos. Thousands of boids may fly in unison patterns,
or scatter and descend into chaos. 
Check out the website at: https://dchen1204.github.io/IMGD4300FinalProject/ 